dct_title_s: Geologic map of the San Bernardino North / north 1/2 of San Bernardino South quadrangles, San Bernardino and Riverside County, California
dct_alternative_sm: San Bernardino North and north 1/2 San Bernardino South map
Geology San Bernardino North and north 1/2 San Bernardino South quadrangles
dct_description_sm: by Thomas W. Dibblee, Jr. ; edited by John A. Minch.
Relief shown by contours and spot heights.

"Topographic base maps from available USGS 7.5-minute quadrangles SAN BERNARDINO NORTH, CA 1967, DMA 2552 III NE -- Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1988; SAN BERNARDINO SOUTH, CA 1967, DMA 2552 III SE -- Series V895, PHOTOREVISED 1980."
Includes quadrangle location map, index to adjacent 7.5 minute quadrangles, and index to sources of geology.
